In re Resignation of Gall.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Gall (1989), 46 Ohio St. 3d 603.]

(No. 89-1709 — Submitted October 11, 1989 — Decided November 1, 1989.)

The resignation of John W. Gall as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
